<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 03:15:34 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>菲律宾热带风暴“八木”造成的死亡人数上升至13人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-death-toll-tropical-storm-yagi-rises-13-2024-09-03/</link><description>热带风暴“八木”已导致菲律宾至少 13 人死亡，周二，马尼拉和附近省份的学校和政府办公室因预期的恶劣天气而关闭。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:39:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-death-toll-tropical-storm-yagi-rises-13-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>股市向美国制造业和就业数据倾斜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-03/</link><description>债券收益率周二走高，而货币和亚洲股市则持稳，因为投资者等待大量数据来确定美国可以降息多少。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 02:25:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>泡菜不再了吗？气候变化使韩国最受欢迎的卷心菜面临风险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kimchi-no-more-climate-change-puts-south-koreas-beloved-cabbage-dish-risk-2024-09-03/</link><description>韩国著名的泡菜正在成为气候变化的受害者，科学家、农民和制造商表示，由于气温上升，用于制作这种随处可见的菜肴的腌制大白菜的质量和数量受到影响。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 01:19:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/kimchi-no-more-climate-change-puts-south-koreas-beloved-cabbage-dish-risk-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>交易员准备迎接劳工数据洪流，美元保持稳定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-brace-labour-data-deluge-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二，美元兑日元和欧元接近两周高点，因投资者准备迎接一系列经济数据，包括周五的美国就业数据，这些数据将影响美联储预期降息的规模。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 01:15:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-steady-traders-brace-labour-data-deluge-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国和南非同意寻求平衡贸易和更多投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-south-africa-sign-cooperation-documents-trade-more-investments-2024-09-03/</link><description>周二的一份联合声明显示，中国和南非的最高领导人在北京会面，同意促进平衡贸易，并讨论促进工商界之间的双向投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 00:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-south-africa-sign-cooperation-documents-trade-more-investments-2024-09-03/</guid></item><item><title>无所畏惧的纳瓦罗在美国公开赛四分之一决赛中迎战复兴的巴多萨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/undaunted-navarro-takes-resurgent-badosa-us-open-quarters-2024-09-02/</link><description>周二，美国网球公开赛在阿瑟·阿什体育场举行第一场四分之一决赛，进入比赛尾声，其中包括艾玛·纳瓦罗 (Emma Navarro) 在内的三名美国人参加了比赛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 21:32:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/undaunted-navarro-takes-resurgent-badosa-us-open-quarters-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰称中国仍是复杂的情报担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-says-china-remains-complex-intelligence-concern-2024-09-02/</link><description>新西兰周二表示，“中国仍然是新西兰的一个复杂的情报问题”，但还有其他国家在该国进行恶意活动。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 21:24:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/new-zealand-says-china-remains-complex-intelligence-concern-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>普京抵达蒙古，这是计划中通往中国的天然气管道的关键环节</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/putin-arrives-mongolia-key-link-planned-gas-pipeline-china-2024-09-02/</link><description>克里姆林宫周一表示，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已抵达蒙古进行国事访问，蒙古位于连接俄罗斯和中国的计划新天然气管道的路线上。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/putin-arrives-mongolia-key-link-planned-gas-pipeline-china-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>国泰航空在发动机零件故障后检查空客 A350 机队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-airways-inspects-a350-fleet-after-identifying-engine-component-2024-09-02/</link><description>香港国泰航空周一表示，在发动机部件在飞行中出现故障后，已开始检查所有空客 A350 飞机，导致英国发动机供应商劳斯莱斯股价大幅下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 14:35:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/cathay-pacific-airways-inspects-a350-fleet-after-identifying-engine-component-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟因中国担忧而收紧氢补贴规则</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-tighten-hydrogen-subsidy-rules-after-china-concerns-2024-09-02/</link><description>欧盟气候变化政策负责人周一表示，在当地企业对廉价的中国进口产品表示担忧后，欧盟委员会正在制定更严格的规则，以确保欧盟对氢能项目的资助有利于欧洲公司。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 13:36:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/eu-tighten-hydrogen-subsidy-rules-after-china-concerns-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉8月中国产电动汽车销量同比增长3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-rise-3-yy-aug-2024-09-02/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周一的数据显示，美国汽车制造商特斯拉的中国制造电动汽车8月份销量同比增长3%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:45:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-china-made-ev-sales-rise-3-yy-aug-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，字节跳动向银行申请 95 亿美元的亚洲美元企业贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-taps-banks-95-bln-asia-dollar-corporate-loan-sources-say-2024-09-02/</link><description>两名知情人士周一表示，TikTok 母公司字节跳动正在向银行申请 95 亿美元贷款，这将是亚洲（日本除外）最大的以美元计价的企业融资。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 12:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/bytedance-taps-banks-95-bln-asia-dollar-corporate-loan-sources-say-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>美元处于守势让全球政策制定者松了口气</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-defensive-brings-relief-policymakers-globally-2024-09-02/</link><description>8月份，美元兑其他主要货币下跌超过2%，创今年最大单月跌幅，为因美元走强而遭受重压的经济体带来一定的缓解。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 11:03:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-defensive-brings-relief-policymakers-globally-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯总统普京表示，他的年轻家庭成员能说流利的普通话</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-says-his-young-family-members-speak-fluent-mandarin-chinese-2024-09-02/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周一表示，他的家庭中的年轻成员能说流利的普通话，不过他告诉学童，尽管汉语日益普及，他们也不应该忘记英语的重要性。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 09:47:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russias-putin-says-his-young-family-members-speak-fluent-mandarin-chinese-2024-09-02/</guid></item><item><title>辛纳在美国公开赛上与进步的保罗发生冲突之前保持谨慎</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-cautious-ahead-clash-with-improved-paul-us-open-2024-09-02/</link><description>美国网球公开赛第四轮将于周一继续进行，世界顶尖选手将在纽约争夺大满贯的荣耀。</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 08:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/tennis/sinner-cautious-ahead-clash-with-improved-paul-us-open-2024-09-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>